---
import SimpleButton from './Button/SimpleButton.astro';
---

<section id="results" class="solution-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">The Solution</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">AI Agents That Collect Better Than Humans</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        Not just cheaper. Actually better at recovering money.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-grid">
      <div class="solution-card highlight">
        <h3>The Numbers Don't Lie</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>25% higher recovery rates</strong> than best human agents</li>
          <li><strong>70% cost reduction</strong> in operations</li>
          <li><strong>10,000 calls per day</strong> with perfect consistency</li>
          <li><strong>Zero turnover</strong> - AI never quits</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="solution-card">
        <h3>Why Debtors Prefer AI</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Infinite patience, never shames</li>
          <li>Offers solutions, not threats</li>
          <li>Available 24/7 at their convenience</li>
          <li>Consistent and professional every time</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="solution-card">
        <h3>How It Works</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Integrates with your existing systems</li>
          <li>Makes thousands of calls simultaneously</li>
          <li>Learns from every conversation</li>
          <li>Escalates complex cases to humans</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="solution-card">
        <h3>Built for LATAM</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Native Spanish & Portuguese</li>
          <li>Understands local dialects</li>
          <li>Compliant with regional laws</li>
          <li>94% address accuracy (vs Google's 70%)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
      <blockquote>
        "Kleva doesn't just save us money. They're actually better at collecting than our best agents. 
        And our customers prefer talking to the AI. It's a win-win-win."
      </blockquote>
      <cite>— Tito, CEO of Vana (100K minutes/month)</cite>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h3>See Kleva in Action</h3>
      <p>Watch how our AI handles real collection calls with empathy and effectiveness.</p>
      <SimpleButton href="/contact" size="lg">
        Get Your Demo
      </SimpleButton>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .solution-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
    background: #dbeafe;
    color: #1e3a8a;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .solution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .solution-card {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .solution-card.highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
    border: 2px solid #3730a3;
  }

  .solution-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .solution-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .solution-card li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .solution-card li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #10b981;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .solution-card li strong {
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .testimonial {
    background: #f3f4f6;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .testimonial blockquote {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #374151;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .testimonial cite {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3730a3 100%);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-box h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
</style>